  <brief_title>Anastomotic Leak Testing in Gastrectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Routine Leak Testing in Radical Gastrectomy on Prevention of Postoperative Anastomotic Leak for Patients With Gastric Cancer: A Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
